- If your pull request solves an issue, please specify it here as e.g: "Solves #<issue-id>". When the pull request is merged, the issue will be closed automatically
- If your pull request is work in progress, please write "[WIP]" in the title to let our CI (and us) knows that you are not ready to merge it
